result.title: 2004 - 2004 Centre for Environment, Fisheries & Aquaculture Science (Cefas) Farn Deeps nephrops 2003/04 - Fisheries Science Partnership
result.name: 2004-2004-centre-for-environment-fisheries-aquaculture-science-cefas-farn-deeps-nephrops-2003-0
result.notes:
Two-trawl survey of the Farn Deeps *Nephrops* ( *Nephrops* *norvegicus* 
) ground, located off the north-east coast of England, undertaken in March, 
November and December 2004. The aims of the survey were to describe the 
composition of the *Nephrops* population in the vicinity of Cefas underwater 
camera survey stations, and to describe the variability of commercial catch 
rates of *Nephrops* and by-catch species according to location, vessel and 
time.
